msgid "MVSim"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Tutorials/Advanced/Simulators/MVSim/Simulation-MVSim.rst:4
msgid ""
"This set of tutorials will teach you how to configure the `MVSim <https://"
"mvsimulator.readthedocs.io/>`__ simulator with ROS 2."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/Tutorials/Advanced/Simulators/MVSim/Simulation-MVSim.rst:6
msgid ""
"MVSim is a lightweight, open-source, multi-vehicle simulator focused on "
"2D+3D visualization of mobile robots. It uses Box2D for 2D rigid body "
"physics and provides realistic vehicle dynamics models (differential drive, "
"Ackermann steering), sensor simulation (2D/3D LiDARs, cameras, IMUs, GPS), "
"and native ROS 2 integration. MVSim is particularly well-suited for testing "
"navigation, SLAM, and multi-robot coordination scenarios with low "
"computational overhead and fast iteration times."
msgstr ""
